This repository is released under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

It reimplements the RLAD method as a plugin on top of the `miles` reinforcement
learning framework (Megatron-LM + SGLang), developed by radixark and released
under the Apache License 2.0:

    https://github.com/radixark/miles

`miles` is NOT vendored in this repository; it is referenced as an external
dependency (a pinned commit + a one-line temperature patch under
train/rl/patches/). See train/rl/REPRODUCTION.md for setup. When you clone
miles, its Apache-2.0 license and NOTICE apply to that code.
